title: 5 Man Rank Solo Queue
body: So I was wondering... will the **dynamic queue** start when season start? I want to know before we get too hyped for it cause me and 3 other friends want to pre-made rank. Will it be released? or do we have to wait til the new champ select is released? Thanks!

replies.body: They haven't announced when it will come out for OCE yet, hopefully soon tho.
